000100 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
000200 PROGRAM-ID. FILEIO.
000300*
000400 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
000500 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
000600 FILE-CONTROL.
000700     SELECT STUDENT-FILE ASSIGN TO "students.dat"
000800         ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL
000900         ACCESS MODE IS SEQUENTIAL
001000         FILE STATUS IS WS-FILE-STATUS.
001100*
001200 DATA DIVISION.
001300 FILE SECTION.
001400 FD  STUDENT-FILE.
001500 01  STUDENT-RECORD.
001600     05  STU-ID      PIC 9(5).
001700     05  STU-NAME    PIC X(20).
001800     05  STU-GRADE   PIC 9(3).
001900*
002000 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
002100 01  WS-FILE-STATUS  PIC XX VALUE SPACES.
002200 01  WS-EOF          PIC X VALUE "N".
002300     88  EOF          VALUE "Y".
002400*
002500 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
002600 MAIN-PARA.
002700     OPEN INPUT STUDENT-FILE.
002800     IF WS-FILE-STATUS NOT = "00"
002900         DISPLAY "FILE OPEN ERROR: " WS-FILE-STATUS
003000         STOP RUN
003100     END-IF.
003200*
003300     PERFORM READ-PARA UNTIL EOF.
003400*
003500     CLOSE STUDENT-FILE.
003600     STOP RUN.
003700*
003800 READ-PARA.
003900     READ STUDENT-FILE
004000         AT END
004100             SET EOF TO TRUE
004200         NOT AT END
004300             DISPLAY STU-ID " " STU-NAME " " STU-GRADE
004400     END-READ.
